==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Florist
<hw>Flo"rist</hw> <pr>(? ⟦or⟧ ?; 277)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>fleuriste</ets>, <ets>floriste</ets>, fr. F. <ets>fleur</ets>
flower. See <er>Flower</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A cultivator of, or
dealer in, flowers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who writes a flora, or an account of
plants.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Floroon</ent>⟦br⟧
